metadata.name: Art Dealer
metadata.description:
Alley 00110111. 
An unknown and strange place where your environment can change without you perceiving it, when you listen to its wings time takes another path and you´re no longer part of it, but you don´t perceive it, it´s like dying, there you can find it. Artworks and objects lost for centuries are exhibited in his street gallery, but there is something different, with time they have changed, like everything that must exist, they have been transformed into what they have gone through, without ceasing to be, it is impossible to cease to be.
Hidden stories and secrets clouded by the passing of life are kept in each of the works, discovered perhaps only when there is no humanity and those who contemplate it is because its plane no longer exists.
